00:00:58.347 --> 00:00:59.668
We've got the tap in and everything.

00:00:59.668 --> 00:01:01.868
We've also got the pop-up
waster already there.

00:01:01.868 --> 00:01:03.262
I always try to put that in first

00:01:03.262 --> 00:01:05.057
