00:01:42.395 --> 00:01:44.223
Just come up here and have a look there.

00:01:44.223 --> 00:01:45.623
And we get our centre.

00:01:45.623 --> 00:01:47.823
So measure across...

00:01:47.823 --> 00:01:49.763
Where you want it to be, in the centre.

00:01:49.763 --> 00:01:51.967
That's 34 inches.

00:01:51.967 --> 00:01:53.342
That's like 17,

00:01:53.342 --> 00:01:54.350
just there.

00:01:54.350 --> 00:01:55.183
Lovely.

00:01:56.466 --> 00:01:57.880
Then use the spirit level

00:01:57.880 --> 00:01:59.825
and score all the way down the wall.

00:01:59.825 --> 00:02:01.007
And then draw a line out

00:02:01.007 --> 00:02:03.535
at a perpendicular angle onto the floor.

00:02:03.535 --> 00:02:05.626
Also line up, make sure
you're about square

00:02:05.626 --> 00:02:06.598
where you wanna be.

00:02:06.598 --> 00:02:08.099
And draw yourself a line out here

00:02:08.099 --> 00:02:11.238
so you know roughly the centre
of your pedestal's gotta be.

00:02:11.238 --> 00:02:14.016
So now we pop this pedestal on the centre.

00:02:14.016 --> 00:02:15.989
On the centre line just there.

00:02:15.989 --> 00:02:18.406
And measure out our distance.

00:02:27.967 --> 00:02:29.640
Once we got that roughly
in the right position

00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:31.580
we can offer up our basin onto there,

00:02:31.580 --> 00:02:32.660
make sure that's level

00:02:32.660 --> 00:02:36.827
and then get our two holes
marked for drilling there.

00:02:38.105 --> 00:02:39.227
Perfect.

00:02:39.227 --> 00:02:40.730
So now we pop our level on here

00:02:40.730 --> 00:02:41.986
and make sure it's all nice and level,

00:02:41.986 --> 00:02:43.263
the bubble's in the middle,

00:02:43.263 --> 00:02:45.694
and then we can go underneath
to mark the two holes.

00:02:45.694 --> 00:02:47.673
They don't really fix it to the wall

00:02:47.673 --> 00:02:48.759
but they do help

00:02:48.759 --> 00:02:50.194
because obviously most of the weight

00:02:50.194 --> 00:02:52.341
is actually on the pedestal foot itself.

00:02:52.341 --> 00:02:54.129
Let's go in there and do that now.

00:02:54.129 --> 00:02:56.662
Right so the hole we're
looking for is just here.

00:02:56.662 --> 00:02:58.345
Let's just get in there

00:02:58.345 --> 00:02:59.512
and mark that.

00:03:03.899 --> 00:03:05.502
Once you've done that on both sides

00:03:05.502 --> 00:03:08.195
I recommend you also put
the waste on quickly now.

00:03:08.195 --> 00:03:09.699
And also measure the height

00:03:09.699 --> 00:03:11.563
you want your waste pipe to be

00:03:11.563 --> 00:03:13.032
if it's not already there.

00:03:13.032 --> 00:03:13.968
Once you've done that,

00:03:13.968 --> 00:03:15.585
you can remove the basin and the pedestal

00:03:15.585 --> 00:03:18.493
and drill a holes through
the brutally hard tiles.

00:03:18.493 --> 00:03:19.652
Right then here we go.

00:03:19.652 --> 00:03:21.412
